{"data":[{"id":562313490,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3b22cc6cdedf456bf95cf56c71132a99","url_token":"xiao-long-69-68","name":"龙嘉昕","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3b22cc6cdedf456bf95cf56c71132a99","user_type":"people","headline":"机械学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":25,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562313490","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546073605,"updated_time":1546183492,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"comment_count":24,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e写在最前:别来我下面两开花，看厌了，见必删。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先回答你的问题:能，而且决不止步于此。可以说这个问题挺荒唐，能问出这个问题说明题主对上清华和证哥猜二者至少其中一个的难度根本没有概念。如果高考上清华的难度是10，竞赛上清华的难度也不过几十，决不上百;而证哥猜的难度是100000+。真的证出哥猜，完全能在全球任一大学数学系直博并出任教授。既然你说自己的方法很简单，先自己给自己发一份，然后给清华大学教授发一份。不用学界普遍认可，只要让教授发现你的研究天赋就足够保送了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是，以上不是重点，以下才是。 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 有没有证明哥猜，不仅会彻底改变学一术界的走向，更会彻底改变你的命运;而改变你命运的力量来自于网络暴力。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e知乎早已不是所谓精英的专场。知乎注册门槛并没有限制学历、品行、性格。随着网络普及，各方面素质参差不齐的用户涌入知乎，网络暴力也大量渗入。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在你拥有两万多关注，我以两万来算。如果你证明了哥猜，你会保有15000~18000关注，并获得直博机会，从事研究工作，几年之内有望十万关注。听起来挺辉煌吧？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可如果你没有证明哥猜呢？(包括没有准时发证明和证明有误。)视你犯错误水平的高低(高中水平到数学系教授水平)，你能保有100~5000关注，有2000~5000人会在第一时间嘲讽辱骂你(是的，有些人就算你水平比他高，只要你失败了，他就会开骂。)，还有80~4500人会持续在你的提问、回答下嘲讽辱骂你，这些你真的能承受吗？\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"写在最前:别来我下面两开花，看厌了，见必删。首先回答你的问题:能，而且决不止步于此。可以说这个问题挺荒唐，能问出这个问题说明题主对上清华和证哥猜二者至少其中一个的难度根本没有概念。如果高考上清华的难度是10，竞赛上清华的难度也不过几十，决不上…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=775\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%